  <h4>PRIMARY REFFERED HOUSE BILLS <small class="badge bg-badge-info">25</small></h4>
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HB00099</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HB00099'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HB00099.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><br /><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Filed: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-01</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Full Title: <span class="font-weight-bold">AN ACT INSTITUTIONALIZING INDUSTRY CLUSTER-BASED PROGRAMS AND PROJECTS THROUGH INTER-LOCAL COOPERATION AND PEOPLE'S PARTICIPATION</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Principal Author/s: <span class="font-weight-bold">1. <a href="../members/search.php?id=acosta-alba" class="font-weight-normal mr-2">ACOSTA-ALBA, MA. LOURDES</a></span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Read: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-23</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Bill Status: <span class="font-weight-bold">Pending with the Committee on PEOPLE S PARTICIPATION since 2019-07-23</span></p></div><div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HB00230</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HB00230'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HB00230.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><br /><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Filed: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-01</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Full Title: <span class="font-weight-bold">AN ACT INSTITUTIONALIZING THE PARTICIPATION OF CIVIL SOCIETY ORGANIZATIONS (CSOS) IN THE PREPARATION AND AUTHORIZATION PROCESS OF THE ANNUAL NATIONAL BUDGET, PROVIDING EFFECTIVE MECHANISMS THEREFOR, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Principal Author/s: <span class="font-weight-bold">1. <a href="../members/search.php?id=vargas-a" class="font-weight-normal mr-2">VARGAS, ALFRED</a></span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Read: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-23</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Bill Status: <span class="font-weight-bold">Pending with the Committee on PEOPLE S PARTICIPATION since 2019-07-23</span></p></div><div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HB00832</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HB00832'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HB00832.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><br /><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Filed: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-01</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Full Title: <span class="font-weight-bold">AN ACT CREATING A SYSTEM OF PARTNERSHIP BETWEEN LOCAL GOVERNMENTS AND CIVIL SOCIETY ORGANIZATIONS THROUGH THE ESTABLISHMENT OF A PEOPLE'S COUNCIL IN EVERY LOCAL GOVERNMENT UNIT, PRESCRIBING ITS POWERS AND FUNCTIONS</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Principal Author/s: <span class="font-weight-bold">1. <a href="../members/search.php?id=bordado-g" class="font-weight-normal mr-2">BORDADO, GABRIEL JR. H.</a></span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Read: <span class="font-weight-bold">2019-07-23</span></p><p class="m-0 p-0">Bill Status: <span class="font-weight-bold">Pending with the Committee on PEOPLE S PARTICIPATION since 2019-07-23</span></p></div><div class='panel-heading'><span class='text-muted text-muted-size'>HB01643</span></div><div class='panel-body'><span class='pull-left m-0 p-0'><a href='#HistoryModal' data-toggle='modal' data-id='#HB01643'  aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample'>[History]</a>&nbsp;<a href="../legisdocs/basic_18/HB01643.pdf" target="_blank" class="mr-1">[Text As Filed]</a></span><div class='clearfix'>&nbsp;</div><br /><p class="m-0 p-0">Date Filed: <sp